00:12:01.302 --> 00:12:07.432
themselves primarily as Scottish, which is up from 57% ten years before.

00:12:08.752 --> 00:12:13.192
In England, it is the opposite, with over half of the population

00:12:13.492 --> 00:12:20.582
identifying as British only and a mere 15% identifying as English.

00:12:21.962 --> 00:12:22.812
Why is this?

00:12:23.222 --> 00:12:27.892
Well, it's not so different really than the reason that someone from

00:12:27.922 --> 00:12:32.902
Barcelona might say that they are Catalan, not Spanish, or even that

00:12:32.912 --> 00:12:37.162
someone from Sicily might tell you that they are Sicilian, not Italian.

00:12:38.032 --> 00:12:43.682
It implies particular pride in where you are from, and that pride is often

00:12:43.682 --> 00:12:48.862
more intense if you are from a smaller part of a larger nation, a part that

00:12:48.862 --> 00:12:53.242
has to fight harder to maintain its own identity, customs and traditions,

00:12:53.692 --> 00:12:58.002
or even a part that believes it should be its own independent country.

00:12:59.672 --> 00:13:06.292
Now, for the past 200 years or so, there has been relative peace between Scotland and England.

00:13:07.182 --> 00:13:12.762
Many Scottish people move to England, especially to London, the capital, where

00:13:12.972 --> 00:13:16.902
there are the most economic opportunities, as we’ll talk about in the next episode.

00:13:17.712 --> 00:13:22.422
There has also been an increasing trend of English people moving to Scotland,

00:13:22.902 --> 00:13:27.502
especially people retiring to Scotland, where house prices are lower, they have

00:13:27.512 --> 00:13:32.222
better access to healthcare and can enjoy the wonderful Scottish countryside.

00:13:33.452 --> 00:13:37.282
Of course, many families are mixed, including mine.

00:13:37.822 --> 00:13:41.772
My mother is English, my father is half Scottish and half Welsh.

00:13:43.132 --> 00:13:47.422
And the rivalry between the two countries, between England and Scotland,

00:13:47.812 --> 00:13:52.992
is now much more one of friendly jokes rather than deep-seated hatred.

