00:15:59.252 --> 00:16:04.402
Now, the relationship between Scotland and England is complex and multi-faceted.

00:16:04.872 --> 00:16:08.112
The two countries have shared a common monarch for over

00:16:08.226 --> 00:16:12.942
400 years, and have been in a political union for 300.

00:16:13.492 --> 00:16:17.532
There is a huge amount of shared cultural heritage, it is probably no

00:16:17.532 --> 00:16:22.292
exaggeration to say that Scottish and English people have more in common

00:16:22.292 --> 00:16:26.892
with each other than with any other nation, English-speaking or otherwise.

00:16:27.812 --> 00:16:32.212
